==================================

I Survived... - Season 3 - SD 480p

==================================


Episode 1 - "Mary / Brooke / Sharene" - December 6, 2009

A young runaway in Modesto, California has her arms cut off in a horrific assault. A pregnant woman and her father flee a deadly firestorm in Australia. A Fallbrook, California woman survives multiple stab wounds in a drug fuelled attack by her enraged boyfriend.


Episode 2 - "Terry / Anne and Debi / Earleen" - December 13, 2009

A Terrell, Texas family suffers multiple tragedy in a deadly home invasion. A California mountain biker is mauled by a mountain lion, and a hotel receptionist in Columbus, Mississippi goes into fight mode to survive a brutal attack by a man posing as a guest.


Episode 3 - "Maggie / Gary / Barbara" - December 20, 2009

A 15-year-old is snatched off the street in Galion, Ohio on an early morning run. A man goes head-to-head with a killer chimpanzee, and a woman working in a restaurant in Davie, Florida is shot and left for dead in a freezer with two slain co-workers.


Episode 4 - "Jessyca / Derek / LaToya" - January 3, 2010

A pregnant woman is attacked in Memphis, Tennessee by her meth-addicted neighbor; an 14-year-old girl from Eau Claire, Wisconsin is kidnapped and held captive by her neighbor, who has sexually assaulted her numerous times before; a Washington state hiker crawls down a mountain after breaking his ankle.


Episode 5 - "Ron and Jill / Randy / Julie" - January 10, 2010

A Fort Worth, Texas couple fight for their lives in a terrifying home invasion. A lineman is electrocuted while working alone up a 35 foot power pole in Rowley, Iowa. And Charlotte, North Carolina a woman makes a desperate dash for safety after being repeatedly stabbed by her ex-boyfriend.


Episode 6 - "Rudrani / Tracey / Teresa" - January 17, 2010

A woman is left for dead when two terrorists storm the Mumbai hotel she is staying in. A 14-year-old saves her brother when their Long Island home is destroyed in a tragic house fire. A Redwater, Texas woman is left permanently scarred in a deadly domestic abuse incident.


Episode 7 - "Verna / Theo / Debra" - January 24, 2010

A single mom living in Ball Ground, Georgia is attacked by an old classmate after spurning his affections. A gold prospector survives five days in the Australian Outback. And a woman is left for dead in the woods outside Fayetteville, North Carolina after being carjacked then shot several times at close range.


Episode 8 - "Christine / Mike / Chris" - Januray 31, 2010

In Fort Lauderdale, Florida A doctor's assistant is violently attacked at home by a former patient she spurned several years earlier. A Georgia man is attacked by a swarm of hornets on the roof of his holiday home and falls down a 100 foot bank. And, a man in Blue Springs, Missouri is shot and assaulted by his girlfriend when he tries to end their relationship.


Episode 9 - "Franklin / Jeff and Frank / Connie" - February 14, 2010

A man and his wife survive a plane crash that killed 125 passengers and crew; a heroic rescue bid goes horribly wrong when 2 police officers are stranded on an iceburg with several other people on frigidly cold Lake Saint Clair; a woman is beaten and left for dead, after 2 men break into her remote East Texas farmhouse and kill her husband.


Episode 10 - "Brandy / Steve / James" - February 21, 2010

In Aurora, Colorado A 16-year-old girl and her deaf friend are abducted and assaulted by two gunmen; a Texas deer hunter drags himself up a dry creek bed after falling out of a tree and breaking both legs; a college student is used as a human shield by a gunman.


=========

I have scoured the Internet for episodes 11-26, but cannot find them available anywhere.
